#CUMBIEPORTAL
For use with web app projects as a starting point

##Deployment Notes
Ensure mod rewrite is enabled for apache by typing `sudo a2enmod rewrite`
You will need to restart the apache server for this to work

Make sure all class files begin with a capital letter.

Ensure a database (using the appropriate settings in /application/config/database.php) is available for use

visit `/migrate` in the browser for automatic database setup.

Ensire `AllowOverride` is enabled in apache by editing `/etc/apache2/apache2.conf` with the following configuration:

It was:
```
<Directory /var/www/>
        Options Indexes FollowSymLinks
        AllowOverride None
        Require all granted
</Directory>
```
and change it to;
```
<Directory /var/www/>
        Options Indexes FollowSymLinks
        AllowOverride All
        Require all granted
</Directory>
```